{"tid":1859921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（繼續舔）WHO秘書長譚德塞：不必暫緩中国旅遊","createTime":"2020-02-03T11:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T05:50:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":231,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"0f22e26d449f20c7e10b582e88d9a43d590ca4a8","tid":1859921,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpXk7cYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpXk7cYr.jpg&h=78727134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）今（3）日重申，不需對中國旅遊和貿易產生「不必要的干擾」，意即不必暫緩中國旅遊和貿易，並稱全球緊密連結是這次疫情爆發的弱點，但也是國際社會的強項。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導 ，世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）今（3）日向國際重申，不需採取措施對中國旅遊和貿易產生「不必要的干擾」，意即不需暫緩對中旅遊及貿易。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞稱：「我們呼籲各國依事實證據來採取一致性的對應政策。全球聯繫是這次疫情爆發的弱點，但同時也是我們最大的力量。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，WHO在本次中國武漢肺炎的疫情處理上步調緩慢，遠不能滿足國際防疫需求，遭外界質疑意圖討好中國。<a href=\"http://更有網友在國際網站change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99change.org&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=40130b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更有網友在國際網站change.org</a>發起連署，要求譚德塞引咎辭職，至今短短幾天已突破20萬人連署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3056374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3056374&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=7e96b0b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3056374&h=79b95c05\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3056374</a>"},{"pid":"ae82410900ef232d0ae5a5c573d84c3ac8150621","tid":1859921,"uid":144626,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:44:25.000Z","msg":"死nigger"},